description: In the desert town called Tull, gunslinger Roland Deschain finally encounters one of the men present at the years-ago death of his first love Susan Delgado. But he may have little time for revenge as his strange quarry, the Man in Black has also come to Tull. He has come to perform wonders-dark and deadly wonders. The first of which is the horrifying resurrection of town drunk Nort through a mystic ritual not meant for human eyes. Why the resurrection of this man and why now is a burning question whose answer could mean certain doom for Roland, last member of the House of Eld.

volume.name: Dark Tower: The Gunslinger - The Battle of Tull

description: Best-selling author Karen Traviss continues to explore the years prior to "Emergence Day." As Marcus Fenix fights what turns out to be the last battle of the Pendulum Wars, his father, Adam, perfects the devastating weapon known as The Hammer of Dawn. Peace is coming to Sera, but neither father nor son is optimistic about its long term prospects.
name: Promise Me

description: The fantastic worlds invented by the visionary writer Wilbur Macken seem to materialize in Darkwood , where monstrous creatures under the orders of the evil sorcerer Koontz sow death and destruction.
name: Il castello nel cielo

description: A self-proclaimed prophet known as The Raven is bringing together all the Indian tribes of the north to give battle to the whites. Thayenda , a Mohawk warrior who joined the Metis Tribe , calls for aid his old sakem Tonka and Zagor . In fact, who is handling the Brotherhood of the Native American is White Moose , chief of the Sioux .
name: Avventura in Canada

description: Zagor tells to Cico and his old friends Sullivans the beginning of his mission as the Darkwood avenger , the first encounter with the head of Delaware Kanoxen and the origin of the eagle symbol on his costume.
name: Darkwood anno zero

description: What is the true age of the guests living in a dilapidated nursing home it is unknown , and Dylan , took office as the custodian , must shed light on the sudden deaths that have just begun .
name: Gli ultimi immortali

description: Between deception and magic tricks Dylan will discover the secret of the beautiful assistant of two powerful magicians .
name: Senza trucco n inganno

description: To prevent the return to Earth of a demon , imprisoned for centuries in the heart of a mountain , Dylan Dog , helped by Bill Porter, a college professor fond of games and puzzles , will have to find a legendary spear that would seem able to kill the evil enemy . The first part of a long and dangerous treasure hunt ...
name: La via degli enigmi

description: To prevent the evil from its triumph , Dylan Dog and Professor Bill Porter will use all their wits to solve the many puzzles placed on the road that leads them to find the only weapon that can stop their infernal enemy : a ruthless demon that makes an art of deception and that seems to have extended them a terrible trap ...
name: L'erede oscuro

description: Trapped in a building , on a floor that should not exist, Dylan Dog and other fellow sufferers find themselves enslaved by mysterious brutal jailers whose only interest is that the construction of the building do not ever stop , or a terrible punishment will occur . To escape from this latest nightmare, the tenant of Craven Road will uncover the terrible secret buried in the heart of that infernal yard.
name: Lavori forzati

description: The journey of Dylan Dog , Groucho and Calista - another " eternal love" of the tenant of Craven Road - to a holiday destination , turns into an odyssey of fear on the streets when, stuck in a terrible traffic jam, the three attend powerless to the collapse of human civilization and the rise of a reign of violence and abuse !
name: I nuovi barbari

description: A ruthless murderer , captured by Dylan Dog when he was a police officer , is now back on the loose because of a futuristic program that can enter the brain of the criminals and clear the evil that resides there . An experiment that seems to fail when the killer disappears and crimes with his signature begin to shed blood on the streets of London. A gruesome trail of death that only the Investigator of Nightmare seems able to stop .
name: Programma di rieducazione
